data.description: SELLER OFFERING up to $5,000 in closing cost or concessions, with approved offer! Interior being painted now! This 3 bedroom / 2 bath home is located at the end of a quiet street, in a cul de sac and on an oversized lot. Home offers open concept, 1,392 sqft split floorplan with large master with walk in closet. Inside laundry with washer & dryer and gas fireplace. Backyard in partially privacy fenced (front) and includes kids playset and above ground pool. This home is looking for new owners!
